		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I actually once sent Quietust email about this and he said it was "by design"... it's still pretty stupid and makes the whole option of disabling sound almost useless. Fortunately Windows Vista and Windows 7 has separate audio volume controls for each application.

		

