	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Because implementing a separate timing system just so you could disable audio wasn't worth the work? It'd be simpler to just send silence to the sound card than implement that.
<br />
<br />The biggest reason to use audio for timing is that if you use video for timing, then audio will have buffer over/underruns. You can only have one master timebase.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


